    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a well-sorted 981-generation Porsche Cayman. This mid-engine platform features a 2.7L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power delivery and an evocative exhaust note. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, complemented by a chassis engineered for neutral handling and high lateral grip. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive fluid service and inspection of the suspension bushings. The atmospheric boxer engine exhibits strong compression and pulls cleanly through the rev range. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited driving.",
