      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with supple leather seats that show minimal bolster wear. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key; I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent oil change, brake pad replacement, and a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires. It shifts smoothly and pulls strong, providing a confident and quiet ride. This is an excellent opportunity for a buyer who values a well-documented history and a car that has been treated with respect.",
